pageContext.description: Dimensions: L 109.2mm; We 39.7; Wm 42.4; Bm 39.3; Blp 7.0; DS 87.5,Typology: rounded body angles; sl. bowed faces; sub. rect. socket, v. sl. waisted, & with narrow flat rect. end - slightly bowed; s. surs. with fine linear structures and granular texture - from core pres.,Manufacture: thin cg. fl. down both sides - little trimmed, hints of it along bl. e.; bumps opp. cg. fl. on interior as well; stumps of two jets on mouth - one broken off too high; parts of inner e. of m. with v. thin lips surfaces with number of irregular mouldings - prob. from cg.; also few hammer dents on one bl. face.,Attached Material: fawn soil - mainly inside socket.
